headline: CPP Investments and Equinix join forces to acquire atNorth to further accelerate growth in the Nordics
summary: atNorth, the leading Nordic high-density colocation and built-to-suit data center provider, today announced that Canada Pension Plan Investment Board (CPP Investments), and Equinix have entered into a joint agreement to acquire atNorth from Partners Group.

headline: CPP Investments and Equinix to Acquire atNorth for US$4 Billion
summary: Canada Pension Plan Investment Board (CPP Investments) and Equinix, Inc. (NASDAQ: EQIX), the world's digital infrastructure company®, today announced they have entered into a joint agreement to purchase atNorth—a leading Nordic high-density colocation and built-to-suit data center provider—from Partners Group, one of the largest firms in the global private markets industry.
